        "id": "01f1332b1666126db43097f90655ae47",
        "content": [
          "Always apply these filters unless the user explicitly says otherwise:\r\n",
          "- IsLowTouch = TRUE\r\n",
          "- HedgeServerID <> 35\r\n",
          "- CID NOT IN (38709216, 38709294, 38709345, 38709389, 38709426)\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "- (IsAirDrop = FALSE AND OpenOrCloseID = 1) OR (OpenOrCloseID = 0)\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "DateID is an integer in YYYYMMDD format. \"Yesterday\" means the most recent DateID value in the table.\r\n",
          "When the user asks for \"trades\" or \"trade count\", use SUM(Click).\r\n",
          "When the user asks for \"volume\", use SUM(Volume) and note it is in USD.\r\n",
          "Join to dim_instrument on InstrumentID to get instrument names (InstrumentDisplayName).\r\n"
        ]
